Hello Manpreet,

I wanted to check in regarding your support ticket 00422806. We haven’t heard from you in a while, and I just wanted to see if you still need assistance with this issue.

If you’re still experiencing problems or have any updates to share, please let me know. If the issue has been resolved, I can go ahead and close the ticket on my end.

Please feel free to reply to this email with any updates or questions. We’re here to help you get the most out of your Netwrix products.

Ticket Number: 00422806
Ticket Subject: Client unable to connect to Test Server
Ticket Details: Hi Team,
We are testing Server version 5.9.4.0 on our Test server. Previously Client machines were connecting to Test Server, but all our Test used cases were failing. Lately the machines are not connecting to test server, even though we tried multiple client versions. Also, we tried clean uninstalling and reinstalling of Clients. Please advise.
Thanks
Manpreet Singh
